{
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": false,
        "iconColor": "#FF5722",
        "name": "AI RCA Events",
        "type": "dashboard",
        "filter": { "ids": [], "tags": ["ai-rca"] }
      }
    ]
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [
    {
      "title": "AI Engine API",
      "url": "http://localhost:8000/api/status",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "external link",
      "targetBlank": true
    },
    {
      "title": "Jaeger",
      "url": "http://localhost:16686",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "external link",
      "targetBlank": true
    },
    {
      "title": "Store (Online Boutique)",
      "url": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "external link",
      "targetBlank": true
    }
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## AI Observability — what this dashboard shows\n\n| Area | Meaning |\n|------|--------|\n| **5xx rate** | Fraction of spans that returned HTTP 5xx per service (0–100%). Spikes often precede RCA. |\n| **P99 latency** | Tail latency from OpenTelemetry span metrics (milliseconds). |\n| **AI cycle** | Time for one full *detect → RCA → remediate* loop. Target **&lt; 15s** (green). Scraped from the AI engine `/metrics` endpoint. |\n| **Throughput** | Span completion rate per service (activity proxy — no Docker CPU metrics here). |\n| **Logs** | Loki streams labeled `service_namespace=online-boutique`. |\n\n**Tip:** Turn on **AI RCA Events** (top) to see orange markers when the engine posts evidence. Open **Jaeger** from the top links to follow `trace_id` in logs."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "HTTP 5xx error rate (by service)",
      "description": "Ratio of 5xx spans to all spans per service. Values are 0–100% (not mixed with latency).",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisLabel": "Error share",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "mode": "none", "group": "A" }
          },
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(duration_milliseconds_count{http_status_code=~\"5..\",service_name!=\"\"}[1m])) / sum by (service_name) (rate(duration_milliseconds_count{service_name!=\"\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "P99 latency (by service)",
      "description": "Tail latency from span histograms (milliseconds).",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 5 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisLabel": "ms",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 6,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "stacking": { "mode": "none", "group": "A" }
          },
          "unit": "ms",
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (service_name, le) (rate(duration_milliseconds_bucket{service_name!=\"\"}[1m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "AI engine — last cycle time (15s budget)",
      "description": "Prometheus scrapes ai-engine:8000/metrics. Green ≤5s, yellow ≤10s, red if over 15s.",
      "type": "gauge",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 5 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 5000 },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 10000 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 15000 }
            ]
          },
          "min": 0,
          "max": 20000,
          "unit": "ms",
          "noValue": "No data yet"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "ai_engine_last_cycle_time_ms",
          "legendFormat": "last_cycle_ms",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Service logs (Loki)",
      "description": "Docker container logs scraped by Promtail with service_namespace=online-boutique. Click a line; use derived fields to open Jaeger if trace_id appears in the log line.",
      "type": "logs",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 11, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 13 },
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "dedupStrategy": "none"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
          "expr": "{service_namespace=\"online-boutique\"}",
          "refId": "A",
          "queryType": "range"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Latency — p50 & p99 (ms)",
      "description": "Same histogram as above; p50 and p99 in milliseconds for readability.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 11, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 13 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisLabel": "Latency (ms)",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "ms",
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (service_name, le) (rate(duration_milliseconds_bucket{service_name!=\"\"}[1m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}} p50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (service_name, le) (rate(duration_milliseconds_bucket{service_name!=\"\"}[1m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}} p99",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Request throughput (spans/s)",
      "description": "Span completion rate from OTel span metrics — indicates which services are busy (not container CPU%).",
      "type": "bargauge",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 24 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "continuous-GrYlRd" },
          "min": 0,
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": { "displayMode": "lcd", "orientation": "horizontal" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "displayMode": "lcd",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "showUnfilled": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(duration_milliseconds_count{service_name!=\"\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": ["ai-observability", "rca", "hackathon"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": { "selected": false, "text": "Prometheus", "value": "Prometheus" },
        "hide": 2,
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "type": "datasource"
      },
      {
        "current": { "selected": false, "text": "Loki", "value": "Loki" },
        "hide": 2,
        "name": "DS_LOKI",
        "query": "loki",
        "refresh": 1,
        "type": "datasource"
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": { "from": "now-15m", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": { "refresh_intervals": ["5s", "10s", "30s", "1m"] },
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "AI Observability - RCA Dashboard",
  "uid": "ai-obs-rca",
  "version": 2,
  "refresh": "10s"
}
